title: What Can We Take Away From This Denver Nuggets Season? | Weekends With Wos
description:
Wos is joined by DNVR Sports’ Adam Mares and they start by discussing how the Nuggets have performed this season despite missing Jamal Murray and Michael Porter Jr. Then they discuss Nikola Jokic’s outstanding season and look ahead to what the Nuggets could look like in the future with their stars healthy.

Host: Wosny Lambre
Guest: Adam Mares
Associate Producer: Isaiah Blakely
